name: CSULB Friend Finder
body:
### Welcome
This webpage is the home of the CSULB Friend Finder app. It is being developed by **Team 2** of the CSULB CECS 491 Tu/Th 7PM class of Spring 2015: **Nicholas Colburn**, **David Garcia**, **Kane Keller**, **Miguel Navarro**, **Tan Tran**, **Gustavo Yepes**, and **Armando Zavala**.

### Project proposal
[Download project proposal (revision 2) here](https://rawgit.com/tktran/csulb-ff/master/proposal.pdf).

### Progress report
[Download Week 1 (9/3-9/10) PR here](https://rawgit.com/tktran/csulb-ff/master/Week01_PR_Fall_2014_T2.xls).

[Download Week 2 (9/11-9/17) PR here](https://rawgit.com/tktran/csulb-ff/master/Week02_PR_Fall_2014_T2.xls).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
